title: NLP Essential Skills-Tom Vizzini and Kimberly McFarland
description:
NLP Essential Skills-Tom Vizzini and Kimberly McFarland	


Sections
1. Tonality - Find your natural voice, speak with power and influence, lead with confidence and emotion
2. Trance and Calibration - Inducing a state in others can get you more than you can imagine
3. Visualization - If you can't see it you can't have it
4. Rapport - How to connect, move, and influence people before you even open your mouth
5. Anchoring - The art of putting a push button on emotions... your own and other peoples
6. Goal Getting - Using your timeline to achieve what you want in life
